data.description: Adorable Craftsman Cottage in 70601! The freshly painted white exterior, boxwood hedges and an adorable front porch greet you as you arrive to enjoy this immaculate historic home conveniently located right across from Barbe Elementary. Inside, you'll find a spacious living room, den with original refinished hardwood floors, dining area, and an open kitchen with a new kitchen island complete with a gas cooktop. All appliances in the kitchen will remain, making meal preparation a breeze and an awesome turn-key opportunity for new home buyers. The home offers 3 large bedrooms and 2 full baths. The master bedroom features an attached bath, newly updated with double vanity, black and white tile, and a walk-in, glass enclosed shower, providing a luxurious spa-like experience. To the rear of the home , a detached storage area has been converted into a large family theatre room, complete with all furnishings and theatre equipment to remain. Previously used as a rentable unit, it is easily converted back into an income producing space, a guest suite, MIL suite, or left just as it is, to be enjoyed by family and guests for movie or gaming nights. There's also a large laundry room with ample storage, and the washer and dryer will remain. Outside, you'll find an outdoor shed that will remain, providing additional storage space for your outdoor equipment and tools. Rounding out this homes abundant offerings is a fully fenced yard with a high wooden privacy fence, perfect for pets and to enjoy the privacy of your large back yard. Don't miss your chance to own this amazing home with numerous updates and plenty of space for entertaining guests and relaxing with family and friends. Schedule your showing today!
